indtallation and set-up of ngrok : (windows)
install chocolatey(package manager for windows): Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))
after that : 1-choco install ngrok
             2-ngrok config add-authtoken 2Zi4AOSdWmzQTM0BE...rest-of-the-token
             3-ngrok http 3000 
             
to create a fixed domain : ngrok http --domain=live-chimp-stunning.ngrok-free.app 3000
                           

after that you visit clerk.com => your application => webhooks => endpoint => add the new fixed endpoint there and make it like this : https://live-chimp-stunning.ngrok-free.app/api/webhooks/clerk


